## Copy Debug Binary to VM

When user says "copy to vm X" or similar, copy the debug binary to the specified VM:

**Source:** `target/debug/grars` (build with `cargo build` if needed)

**Destination:** `~/.local/bin/grars` on all VMs

**Process:**
1. Build debug binary: `cargo build` (if not already built)
2. SCP to VM: `scp -P <PORT> target/debug/grars vboxuser@localhost:/tmp/grars`
3. SSH and replace: `ssh -p <PORT> vboxuser@localhost "cp /tmp/grars ~/.local/bin/grars && chmod +x ~/.local/bin/grars"`


